00:41:25.230 --> 00:41:27.340
Maestro, Maestro.

00:41:46.520 --> 00:41:49.060
Comandante Gu, lamento molestarlo.

00:41:52.040 --> 00:41:52.650
Yangshan,

00:41:53.670 --> 00:41:56.420
